<section class="section bg-white">
	<div class="section-content py4">
		<div class="md-flex full-bleed-two-column">
			<div class="flex-item col col-12 md-col-9 pxr1">
				<h2 class="h2-variation-1"> IT professionals are challenged like never before in the modern digital business. </h2>
				<p>
					In your IT role, you are not only expected to support new digital applications and services, but do so under tight budgets while complying with corporate and government policies.
				</p>
				<p>
					As new technology is introduced every day, you need to find ways to simplify the workload to deal with added complexity. You must optimize the use of both existing as well as new technologies such as mobile apps and the cloud, while ensuring security of the IT environment.
				</p>
			</div>
			<div class="flex-item col col-12 md-col-3 layout-secondary-flex-item padding-bottom-0">

				<section>
					<h3>Modernizing IT Operations in Response to Digital Change</h3>
