<section>
	<div class="tab-wrapper bg-corduroy">
		<h2 class="m0 text-center white">4 benefits of digital transformation</h2>
		<ul class="tabs-nav bg-corduroy center-block overflow-none flex-table">
			<li class="p2 flex-cell n-col-4">
				<a class="white bold no-scroll" href="#tab-377575361"> Increase Productivity </a>
			</li>
			<li class="p2 flex-cell n-col-4">
				<a class="white bold no-scroll" href="#tab-377575671"> Ensure Security </a>
			</li>
			<li class="p2 flex-cell n-col-4">
				<a class="white bold no-scroll" href="#tab-377575061"> Manage Complexity </a>
			</li>
			<li class="p2 flex-cell n-col-4">
				<a class="white bold no-scroll" href="#tab-377574601"> Focus on the Customer </a>
			</li>
		</ul>

		<div id="tab-377575361" class="section bg-seashell">

			<div class="section-content flex-tab">
				<h2> Do more with less by harnessing the power of automation </h2>
				<div class="md-flex ">
					<div class="flex-item col col-12 md-col-4   fixed-width-flex-item  imageContainer ">
						<img class="" src="http://media.cms.bmc.com/images/Increase_Productivity.png" alt="" title=""></img>
					</div>

					<div class="flex-item col col-12 md-col-8">
						<div class="tab-content-wrapper">

							<p>
								<a href="/it-solutions/digital-enterprise-automation.html">Digital enterprise automation</a> is crucial in organizations with complex IT environments, particularly&nbsp; when data is coming in from multiple sources &ndash; from local systems, to public clouds, to Internet of Things sensors. More than 60% of users of enterprise automation report a better customer experience, lower costs, better integration of data with their big data initiatives, and improvement in the way their virtual and cloud environments are managed.
							</p>
							<p>
								See how these BMC solutions can help:
							</p>
							<ul class="orange-tick-bullets">
								<li>
									<b><a href="/it-solutions/control-m.html">Control-M Workload Automation:</a></b> Automate diverse batch application workloads while reducing failure rates, improving SLAs, and accelerating application deployment.
								</li>
								<li>
									<b><a href="/it-solutions/bladelogic-server-automation.html">BladeLogic Server Automation:</a></b> Rapidly remediate known vulnerabilities, and automate compliance checks.
								</li>
								<li>
									<b><a href="/it-solutions/cloud-lifecycle-management.html">Cloud Lifecycle Management:</a></b> Orchestrate the delivery and management of secure IT services across private and public clouds, as well as legacy data center infrastructures.
								</li>
								<li>
									<b><a href="/it-solutions/atrium-orchestrator.html">Atrium Orchestrator:</a></b> Automate common, repeatable tasks to significantly lower costs and reduce the risk associated with manual interactions.
								</li>
							</ul>

						</div>
					</div>

				</div>
			</div>

		</div>
		<div id="tab-377575671" class="section bg-seashell">

			<div class="section-content flex-tab">
				<h2> Leverage automation to achieve a secure IT infrastructure </h2>
				<div class="md-flex ">
					<div class="flex-item col col-12 md-col-4   fixed-width-flex-item  imageContainer ">
						<img class="" src="http://media.cms.bmc.com/images/Ensure_Security.png" alt="" title=""></img>
					</div>

					<div class="flex-item col col-12 md-col-8">
						<div class="tab-content-wrapper">

							<p>
								Attacks by hackers are on the rise, with more sophisticated ways to gain entry into corporate networks. It is imperative that IT professionals secure their IT infrastructure against attacks to keep the digital enterprise up and running.
							</p>
							<p>
								See how these BMC solutions can help:
							</p>
							<ul class="orange-tick-bullets">
								<li>
									<b><a href="/it-solutions/bladelogic-threat-director.html">BladeLogic Threat Director:</a></b> Keep both security and operations teams aware of any potential security threats.
								</li>
								<li>
									<b><a href="/it-solutions/bladelogic-server-automation.html">BladeLogic Server Automation:</a></b> Immediately and automatically deliver security patches to servers when needed.
								</li>
							</ul>

						</div>
					</div>

				</div>
			</div>

		</div>
		<div id="tab-377575061" class="section bg-seashell">

			<div class="section-content flex-tab">
				<h2> Simplify management of your IT infrastructure </h2>
				<div class="md-flex ">
					<div class="flex-item col col-12 md-col-4   fixed-width-flex-item  imageContainer ">
						<img class="" src="http://media.cms.bmc.com/images/Manage_Complexity.png" alt="" title=""></img>
					</div>

					<div class="flex-item col col-12 md-col-8">
						<div class="tab-content-wrapper">

							<p>
								With limited headcount and resources at your disposal, you need solutions that are easy to manage and make everyday operations scalable. Swivel-chair management of the past can be eliminated by aggregating different workflows and processes under a few management interfaces.
							</p>
							<p>
								See how these BMC solutions can help:
							</p>
							<ul class="orange-tick-bullets">
								<li>
									<b><a href="/it-solutions/control-m.html">Control-M Workload Automation:</a></b> Schedule and monitor complex business processes from one easy-to-use interface.
								</li>
								<li>
									<b><a href="/it-solutions/bladelogic-threat-director.html">BladeLogic Threat Director:</a></b> Keep both security and operations teams aware of any potential security threats.
								</li>
								<li>
									<b><a href="/it-solutions/atrium-orchestrator.html">Atrium Orchestrator:</a></b> Automate common, repeatable tasks to significantly lower costs and reduce the risk associated with manual interactions.
								</li>
								<li>
									<b><a href="/it-solutions/cloud-lifecycle-management.html">Cloud Lifecycle Management:</a></b> Orchestrate the delivery and management of secure IT services across private and public clouds, as well as legacy data center infrastructures.
								</li>
							</ul>

						</div>
					</div>

				</div>
			</div>

		</div>
		<div id="tab-377574601" class="section bg-seashell">

			<div class="section-content flex-tab">
				<h2> Deliver digital services in a way users expect </h2>
				<div class="md-flex ">
					<div class="flex-item col col-12 md-col-4   fixed-width-flex-item  imageContainer ">
						<img class="" src="http://media.cms.bmc.com/images/Focus_on_Customer.png" alt="" title=""></img>
					</div>

					<div class="flex-item col col-12 md-col-8">
